"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-7-24-paris-olympics-2024-tennis-djokovic-alcaraz-headline-top-players-to-watch\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Summer Games are stacked with a superstar lineup of tennis players in the men's and women's tournaments.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Tennis will be one of the most highly anticipated Olympic events atParis 2024, with a superstar cast of players targeting gold.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From stars new to old, the competition will be fierce in both the men's and women's tournaments.\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are five of the top contenders for gold at the Paris Olympics 2024:  Alcaraz is the clear favourite for gold in the men's singles, having won the 2024 French Open at Roland-Garros - which doubles up as the same clay court venue for the Paris Olympics tournament.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8941750102292745e-17, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also stormed to a fourth career Grand Slam title at Wimbledon on July 14, beatingNovak Djokovic in straight setsin the final.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9982297053602579, \"rank\": 0.0017734341249069521, \"text\": \"career Grand Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_(tennis)\"}, {\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.790122166987570